OL,3,C'I couldn't think clearly' - kayaker
OL,4,Crescued from treacherous cove
OL,6,FMatt told ITV's Jacquie Bird he went
OL,7,Finto 'panic mode' when he fell out of
OL,8,Fhis kayak.
OL,10,FA man who was saved by the RNLI in
OL,11,FNorth Devon says he went into "panic
OL,12,Fmode" when he fell out of his kayak
OL,13,Fnear Ilfracombe.
OL,15,FMatt Windsor was rescued in just seven
OL,16,Fminutes after a mayday call to the
OL,17,Flifeboat crews. As they approached
OL,18,Fhim, he told them how shaken up he was
OL,19,Fby the experience.
