OL,3,C'I couldn't think clearly' - kayaker
OL,4,Crescued from treacherous cove
OL,6,FSpeaking afterwards, he said: "The
OL,7,Fwater was so cold, that instantly put
OL,8,Fme in panic mode.
OL,10,F"The cold water shock, I instantly
OL,11,Fbreathed in when I hit the water and
OL,12,Fswallowed loads of sea water and it
OL,13,Fjust made everything so much more
OL,14,Fdifficult. I couldn't think clearly, I
OL,15,Fwas panicking more."
OL,17,FHe was in the water for 40 minutes,
OL,18,Fstruggling to get back on his kayak,
OL,19,Fwhen he pressed the mayday button on
OL,20,Fhis radio.
