OL,3,C'I couldn't think clearly' - kayaker
OL,4,Crescued from treacherous cove
OL,6,FMatt said: "If they hadn't shown up
OL,7,Fthat day things could have been very
OL,8,Fdifferent. I was cold, I was
OL,9,Fexhausted. Them coming out means I'm
OL,10,Fhere today."
OL,12,FRNLI figures show lifeboats were
OL,13,Flaunched 15 hundred times around the
OL,14,FSouth West's coastline last year, with
OL,15,Fnearly 80 lives saved. That's a six
OL,16,Fper cent increase in call-outs.
OL,18,FRNLI mechanic Stuart Carpenter was one
OL,19,Fof the people to rescue Matt that day.
OL,20,FHe said people shouldn't be afraid to
OL,21,Fcall for help.
