OL,4,Crescued from treacherous cove
OL,6,FStuart said: "We're much happier for
OL,7,Fpeople to call us when they think
OL,8,Fthey're in trouble.
OL,10,F"It's brilliant for us if we get there
OL,11,Fand it's all sorted and they're safe -
OL,12,Fthat's the best result was can have."
OL,14,FThe RNLI costs #500k a day to run
OL,15,Facross the country - funded solely off
OL,16,Fdonations.
OL,18,FThis month they're calling on people
OL,19,Fto do the to help raise money. To get
OL,20,Finvolved, you need to cover a mile
OL,21,Fevery day in May - however you want.
